Download the latest Neo4j Server installation file from the Neo4j website: http://www.neo4j.org/download

Double click the exe file to install Neo4j server

Open Neo4j Community

Windows “star” ->> “All Programs” ->> “Neo4j Community” 

By default it selects c:\Users\[username]\Documents\Neo4j\default.graphdb. You can change your path to a different directory if you want.

Click the "Start" button.

Once the server starts, we can observe that many files are generated under the specified directory.

Access Neo4j by using http://localhost:7474/
